MY LOVE FOR YOU
My love for you can never turn cold
My love for you can never grow old
My love for you can never fade
My love for you can never be dead
My love for you is unconditional
My love for you is always special
My love for you is through thin and thick
My love for you is as hard as a brick
My love for you is for real
My love for you can never be killed
My love for you is above the law
My love for you is very pure
My love for you is always strong
My love for you can never go wrong
My love for you does not last with my breath
My love for you goes on after my death
